A tool to display git repository statuses in a table format

Usage: git-statuses [OPTIONS] [DIR]

Arguments:
  [DIR]
          Directory to scan
          
          [default: .]

Options:
  -a, --all
          Recursively scan all subdirectories

  -r, --remote
          Show remote URL

  -s, --summary
          Show a summary of the scan

  -h, --help
          Print help

  -V, --version
          Print version
